title.narrative: Peace and Development Project (1st Phase APL)

description.narrative: This additional financing remains with the same objectives as the original project: to assist vulnerable, low-income and displaced populations in rural and urban communities in the conflict affected region in order to reduce the risk of their exposure to conflict and mitigate the negative impact of possible derived effects.
